{"tid":2146043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來香港賣緊嘅美國冰鮮豬都係支那公司","createTime":"2020-08-08T10:46:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T11:13:23.000Z","uid":183758,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ae74808f29c7ee5bfdae3e2e0e44ca0d14d6d559","tid":2146043,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T10:46:55.000Z","msg":"史密斯菲爾德食品（英語：Smithfield Foods），是全球最大的豬肉養殖商、生產商及加工商。史密斯菲爾德食品公司在美國擁有多種肉製品品類及產品品牌，並在全球12個國家開展業務。公司成立於1936年，總部位於美國維吉尼亞州小鎮史密斯菲爾德。全球員工約58100人，公司每年養殖約1500萬頭豬，一年屠宰2700萬頭。該公司於2013年9月26日被中華人民共和國的萬洲國際集團以71億美元價格收購，現為萬洲國際的全資子公司，2014年開始使用中文品牌「史蜜斯」。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n萬洲國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好彩而家美國瞓醒 支共真係無孔不入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161723b84c8eac3ce3dbe3368c25c2bdafa85a5b","tid":2146043,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T10:47:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n制裁"},{"pid":"b95fb11a0d756a45c056d7702ff1ef6ccd2c6506","tid":2146043,"uid":268537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T10:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"136df06a548a7b62ee4285876ec74551cf30d27a","tid":2146043,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T10:49:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa